{
  "stem": "21582.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "You know, there was-- there, there, there were theaters in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "There were hidden library-- books.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Where my-- that's all I remember my father spent a great deal of time of was just sitting near the stove when we had wood and, and, and just reading.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He lost a lot of weight.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] [SIGHS] Well, there were theaters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And we supported the theaters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Also, a lot of poetry was written during the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "My sister-- I will share the book with you later-- wrote a book about-- she collected the poetry written in-- during the war in Warsaw Ghetto, both in Yiddish and in Polish, and translated them and added commentaries about them to set them into the-- into the setting, into the framework of the times.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then I'll come back now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "There were theaters.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And, and, and, and, and now I will come back to, to, to the schools.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the very early schools, where we called them [NON-ENGLISH]-- and that means 'gardens.' The first attempt-- the first direction that the community focused on is save the children.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, at the very beginning, saving the children meant saving the best in them, saving the most humane in them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so, little schools that did not have exactly-- there wasn't that much emphasis on, on instructions as it was to let the children play.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Let, let the children sing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let the children feel, feel the air of freedom.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And let them be children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then-- that stopped very, very quickly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I, I don't know whether it was because the funds ran out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I doubt that very much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think, and I am not certain, that anything that was organized was suspicious.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
